(6323, 'Leave it to the dwarves to send a mining specialist from Ironforge to tell us how to mine.  How hard is it to take a pick and chip away at some rock?  Well, since he\'s here, he\'s probably the one you should see anyhow.  His name is Gelman and he resides over in the Dwarven District.', 'Leave it to the dwarves to send a mining specialist from Ironforge to tell us how to mine.  How hard is it to take a pick and chip away at some rock?  Well, since he\'s here, he\'s probably the one you should see anyhow.  His name is Gelman and he resides over in the Dwarven District.', 6323, 0, 0, 0, 0, 256, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27481),
